<lb n="0667a29" ed="T"/>數還來墮諸惡趣受生死苦。若能常念如是
<pb n="0667b" ed="T" xml:id="T17.0765.0667b"/>
<lb n="0667b01" ed="T"/>一法，我證彼定得不還果，不復還來生此
<lb n="0667b02" ed="T"/><note n="0667001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔世〕－【宮】＊</note><note n="0667001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">世【大】＊，〔－〕【宮】＊</note><app n="0667001"><lem wit="【大】">世</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>間。是故我說：若諸有情能念一法，我證
