<lb n="0667c12" ed="T"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgT17p0667c1201" style="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em"><l>「我觀諸有情，<caesura/>由不<note n="0667006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">念安般＝安般故【宋】【元】【宮】</note><note n="0667006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">念安般【大】，安般故【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="0667006"><lem wit="【大】">念安般</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】 【宮】">安般故</rdg></app>，</l>
